msgstr "Alcune alternative popolari includono:"

#: ../../dns_over_http.rst:23 603980665cfa42be8b5b9d5dc417480b
msgid ""
"`Quad9 <https://dns.quad9.net/dns-query>`_, privacy-focused with malware "
